title: Michelle Wie Eats Live Squid, Posts Video on Instagram
text:
Michelle Wie Eats Live Squid, Posts Video on Instagram Golf 1 day ago Extra Spin Staff © Golf
For some reason, Michelle Wie ate live squid and then posted a video of her doing so on her Instagram page.
AdChoices We are not sure exactly why she did this, but she’s always been pretty active on social media. Her recent posts even show her eating pig feet and jellyfish not long ago.
There was also the time she twerked after winning the U.S. Open , dyed her hair blonde and, recently, dyed her hair nearly every color of the rainbow and then rocked pink sneakers at the Evian Championship.
Anyway, here’s a video of Wie eating live squid. That is, if you are brave enough to watch.
Hahahaha I mean....I gotta do it! Only in Korea once a year with the fam bam! #livesquid #bizarrefoodskorea #fearfactor
A video posted by Michelle Wie (@themichellewie) on Oct 18, 2015 at 1:33am PDT
